title: DEL SKATEBOARD Deck
description:
Del The Funky Homosapien drops in to give an update on the limited edition skateboard decks he designed with Arnette.

The limited edition Del x Arnette skate decks feature an oversized Hieroglyphics logo over stained wood and a repeating Arnette A-wing logo. Available in two sizes, 8.25 inches and 8 inches wide, they'll be available exclusively at Del shows.
